EN: You need to control your calorie intake.

ZH: 健康饮食应该注意热量的摄取。
EN: A healthy diet should pay attention to calorie intake.

ZH: 运动可以帮助你消耗热量。
EN: Exercise can help you burn calories.

ZH: 热量是能量的一种单位。
EN: Calories are a unit of energy.

ZH: 大多数零食含有很高的热量。
EN: Most snacks contain high levels of calories.

ZH: 这种饮料提供了大量的热量。
EN: This drink provides a significant amount of calories.

ZH: 每个人每天所需的热量不同。
EN: The required calorie intake varies for each person.

ZH: 吃水果比吃巧克力含更少的热量。
EN: Eating fruit has fewer calories than eating chocolate.

ZH: 低热量食物更适合减肥。
EN: Low-calorie foods are better for weight loss.

ZH: 吃太多高热量食物容易导致肥胖。
EN: Eating too many high-calorie foods can lead to obesity.

ZH: 控制饮食热量是减肥的第一步。
EN: Controlling calorie intake is the first step in weight loss.

